Introducing the So Kind ARTed Curriculum ✨
 We have partnered with Slam Out Loud to bring kindness back to school through art. 🎨💛

We are so proud to present The Kindness Curriculum, a 6-module video-based curriculum taught by our in-house Kindness Professor, Ms. Ananya! The curriculum is designed to use creativity and social-emotional learning to help kids aged 9-15 build emotional awareness, kindness, and connection, all through poetry, painting, and self-expression!

The curriculum will reach children across cities in India through Slam Out Loud’s Jijivisha Fellowship and Arts for All Program. For all our Parents and Educators around the world - The Modules are now available on So Positive’s YouTube Channel - check the link in our Bio! 

We are so happy to finally be sharing a piece of our heart with everyone. 
Because every child deserves a safe space to feel, express, and grow! 🌻💛

#SoKindARTed #SoPositive #SlamOutLoud #KindnessCurriculum #MentalHealthMatters #ArtForChange #AnanyaPanday #EmotionalWellbeing #EducationThroughArt #SocialEmotionalLearning
